			                                                    <p><p class="quickhit">President Obama said yesterday that he <a
href="http://links.heritage.org/ct/10568184:13977999709:m:1:282730454:788C7BB8A7C21A604B9944E727F63D53:r">“won’t compromise”</a> on the fiscal cliff when it comes to
raising taxes.</p>
<p class="quickhit">More than 150 companies “have declared special dividends totaling about $20 billion this quarter to <a
href="http://links.heritage.org/ct/10568185:13977999709:m:1:282730454:788C7BB8A7C21A604B9944E727F63D53:r">avoid anticipated tax increases</a> in 2013,” reports Bloomberg.</p>
<p class="quickhit">The Associated Press reports that a new fee has surfaced in the latest Health and Human Services regulations for Obamacare.
Employers will have to pay $63 per employee per year into a fund to cover <a
href="http://links.heritage.org/ct/10568186:13977999709:m:1:282730454:788C7BB8A7C21A604B9944E727F63D53:r">pre-existing conditions</a>, mainly for patients in the individual
insurance market.</p>
<p class="quickhit">Some Michigan schools are closed today after <a href="http://links.heritage.org/ct/10568182:13977999709:m:1:282730454:788C7BB8A7C21A604B9944E727F63D53:r"
target="_blank">teachers unions called in sick</a> to protest the right-to-work law.</p>
<p class="quickhit">What do you think about the filibuster? Should Senators have the right to speak at length against legislation? Join us at 11 a.m.
ET for an event on this topic that you can <a href="http://links.heritage.org/ct/10568187:13977999709:m:1:282730454:788C7BB8A7C21A604B9944E727F63D53:r">watch online</a>.</p>
